oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Annie White [by Flavius J. Fisher]
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: [Flavius J. Fisher]
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Crayon art drawing, believed to be Annie White, ca. 1857. Annie White was the daughter of Hugh A.M. White and the wife of James Dickinson Cowan. Attributed to artist Flavius J. Fisher.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Drawings; Art; Portraits;
